{"tid":591571,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[最後2個]17-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃16強次回合投選專區 #Mina 謝安琪 林明禎 Momo","createTime":"2018-03-13T15:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T16:59:14.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec601585f69a11b471d1a098b67ea544b7272ed","tid":591571,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n名井南@TWICE v 謝安琪<br />\n林明禎 v 平井桃@TWICE<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=Ba%2FAR15Kc9TwbmNb8EA4s3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=81c4df47\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089de22d37a737d77cfd66cbe174aff2d10d8c4d","tid":591571,"uid":92376,"like":48,"dislike":74,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG環球女神冠軍盃16強次回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-3-14 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NtFSsxA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNtFSsxA.png&h=93e6c847&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zCo0EEy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzCo0EEy.png&h=fb8364fd&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fDKJUOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfDKJUOh.png&h=cf9c1fd7&s={SIZE}\" />名井南@TWICE v 謝安琪<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0Q6FBnk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0Q6FBnk.png&h=d7f5937a&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(首回合 57-91)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">環冠盃淘汰賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合賽事設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可再獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"3ff23fb02f9cae27f477e66402e2a2cecf072fb4","tid":591571,"uid":92376,"like":68,"dislike":54,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-3-14 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/AjhEHM9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAjhEHM9.png&h=b7d0a6c2&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0LpKKbD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0LpKKbD.png&h=0a63a2ed&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/mS94Fjr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmS94Fjr.png&h=c47132c2&s={SIZE}\" />林明禎 v 平井桃@TWICE<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fDKJUOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfDKJUOh.png&h=cf9c1fd7&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(首回合 72-79)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">環冠盃淘汰賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合賽事設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可再獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"2fb72d3937f29fb3b561a4e13bb2e1d903afad3d","tid":591571,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T16:03:45.000Z","msg":"環冠八強頭六位晉級女神如下<br />\nGal Gadot<br />\n朱千雪<br />\nIU<br />\n周子瑜@TWICE<br />\n新垣結衣<br />\n林宣妤<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04fba61c38cd34b628f4a3d73c480f940e3db49","tid":591571,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T16:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b06f906a81f49641a9d8a0767a4a0c9bbbfa5e1","tid":591571,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T16:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c55ebc05f26eef0c7d391f70e4a2c5cfdfb0331","tid":591571,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T16:13:30.000Z","msg":"環冠八強頭六位晉級女神如下<br />\nGal Gadot -以色列<br />\n朱千雪 -香港<br />\nIU -韓國<br />\n周子瑜@TWICE -台灣<br />\n新垣結衣 -日本<br />\n林宣妤 -馬來西亞<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c8a914723153592441389fb25f9e3993d3e455","tid":591571,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T16:14:35.000Z","msg":"以上六強睇落分佈暫時好平均，無乜大戶<br />\n就算計埋呢兩場目前形勢，應該係香